data.description: This house comes with all the space with even best views! Over 3000 square feet sitting on 2.5 acres this is a country dream come true. 3 bedrooms on the left side of the home with 3 full bathrooms. Closed in sun room for a huge 2nd living area. Added on the right side of the home is 3 additional rooms that could be bedrooms, office space, or craft or flex space. Storage shed and SHOP with electric in the back yard. Wylie ISD but NO city taxes as this property is outside city limits.
